Description: This beautiful electric guitar kit contains the following: 1) Schecter Damien Special Electric Guitar with Floyd Rose Tremolo, Black - see Amazon product number B008QVR1Q6 for the detailed reviews. The guitar is shiny and gorgeous, in excellent condition. Here is the description from Amazon: The Floyd Rose Special is the authentic version of a licensed Floyd Rose tremolo system. It maintains the features of an Original Floyd Rose, while utilizing zinc alloy saddles in place of steel and a zinc alloy sustain block in place of brass.EMG Active 81/85 PickupsThe Maple top transfers a bright tone to the body which complements the warm tones of a mahogany body. Maple has a uniform grain, it’s strong and stable, and it has less reaction from environmental changes than other hardwoods.The Rosewood fretboard is naturally oily, and works well for any surface that sees frequent human contact. The sound is richer in fundamental than Maple because the stray overtones are absorbed into the oily pores.Grover tuners 2) Schecter Guitar Research Diamond Series Molded Guitar Case - see Amazon product number B001U5NYD4 for details, this item alone sells for $150 on Amazon. The case is in excellent condition with tags still on it as you can see from the photos. Rugged, rectangular molded exteriorPlush interior with shaped bed for all Diamond Series guitarsDrawbar latches 3) Levy's Leathers DM17-BLK Genuine Leather Guitar Strap, Black, in like-new condition, see Amazon product number B003MQN8LM, this strap sells for $25 on Amazon: 2 1/2 inch leather guitar strap.Adjustable from 38 inches to 53 inches.Also available in extra long (XL), which adds 12 inches to overall length. 4) Levy's Leathers MSSC8-BLK Signature Series Cotton Guitar Strap, Black, in excellent condition, see Amazon product B000XPO0IU for details and reviews. 2 inch Signature Series cotton guitar strap with suede ends and tri-glide adjustment.Adjustable to 54 inches.Also available in extra long (XL), which adds 12 inches to overall length.2- Inch WideMade of CottonSuede EndsTri-Glide AdjustmentAdjustable up to 54- Inch 5) Korg AW-2 Clip-On Tuner, see Amazon product number B001XJBWXG for details on a very similar tuner. 6) Guitar picks, mouth tuner, guitar bar and wrenches for the Floyd Rose feature. Also, the keys for the guitar case. Notes on condition: the guitar was played very little, estimating a total of 4 to 5 hours playing time. My cousin claimed the 6th string (thinnest string) was out of tune and attempted to tune the string like a traditional guitar, by cranking the tuning knob at the top of the guitar without loosing the top bracket with the provided wrench. He never seen a Floyd Rose guitar before. So, the thin 6th string broke between the tuning knob and the top bracket, so the 6th string will need to eventually be replaced (interestingly, the 6th string is actually still playable and may still be in tune due to the Floyd Rose feature).
